research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Santa Fe, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government, which is categorized as 'mayor_council' for the purpose of this request. The Mayor and five Council members are elected at large. Ronald "Bubba" Jannett also holds the role of Mayor Pro Tem. Some search results for 'Santa Fe' referred to Santa Fe, New Mexico, but were excluded as the prompt specified 'Santa Fe city, tx'.
